name: Spring Nature Walk
description: Join us for a guided nature walk to discover the beauty of spring flora and fauna in the park!

name: Community Health Fair
description: Get free health screenings, learn about healthy lifestyle choices, and enjoy fun activities for the whole family at our annual health fair!

name: Volunteer Day at the Animal Shelter
description: Help us care for and socialize with our furry friends at the shelter. No experience necessary!

name: Youth Leadership Summit
description: Join us for a day of workshops, speakers, and networking opportunities to empower young leaders to make a positive impact in their communities!

name: Earth Day Cleanup
description: Help us clean up the local park and waterways to protect our planet and wildlife!

name: Beach Cleanup Day
description: Join us for a day of cleaning up the beach and keeping our oceans clean! Bring your own gloves and bags if you can.

name: Mental Health Awareness Symposium
description: Join us for a day of discussion and education about mental health and how to support those struggling with mental health issues.

name: Charity Walk for Cancer Research
description: Join us for a walk to raise funds for cancer research! All proceeds go towards finding a cure for cancer.

name: Coding Bootcamp
description: Join us for a week-long intensive coding bootcamp to learn programming fundamentals and web development skills!

name: Community Garden Day
description: Join us for a day of gardening and community building at the local community garden. All ages and experience levels welcome!
